{"tid":1045820,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如何有動力做自己唔想做既野？","createTime":"2019-03-03T19:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T05:44:19.000Z","uid":240321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"30e0cdb4c7e24d25f99023eaeb0cc4f46d444a0f","tid":1045820,"uid":240321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T19:36:41.000Z","msg":"第一次開post 錯台請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本因爲鐘意畫畫等讀左視覺傳意<br />\n但讀到中途發現學既野不如人意<br />\n交緊功課既主題都係比老師改完又改過，結果同原本自己既理念一啲都唔同<br />\n有同屋企人講過但佢地都叫我繼續讀落去只少拎張證書都好<br />\n<br />\n事到如今已經覺得做呢啲功課好痛苦<br />\n已經對GPA、功課進度之類無心裝載 好頹<br />\n但唔繼續落去又怕辜負屋企人既期望<br />\n<br />\n請問各位有無啲方法可以有動力迫做到一啲唔想做既事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬧下幾句都好 比我清醒下我應該要堅持既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b3ca85719ae301bfdbebd5de629de4207faef2","tid":1045820,"uid":130596,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T19:41:33.000Z","msg":"條路自己揀 仆街唔好喊"},{"pid":"fce83c9548c6b27805f21e1b85fa253c33fc002a","tid":1045820,"uid":130093,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T19:58:29.000Z","msg":"毋忘初衷啦<br />\n<br />\n人生就好似跨越一座座高山咁，的確係辛苦，但係需要你一步步腳踏實地去行<br />\n<br />\n你試下全心全意擺副心機落去先，當試練又好、<br />\n<br />\n磨練又好，當你努力之後見到一個好靚嘅風景，再<br />\n<br />\n回頭望住自己昔日停留嘅山丘，就會好感激當初自<br />\n<br />\n己嘅堅持"},{"pid":"691054724eac1187ddd299052e59844673566731","tid":1045820,"uid":240321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04b3ca85719ae301bfdbebd5de629de4207faef2","tid":1045820,"uid":130596,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T19:41:33.000Z","msg":"條路自己揀 仆街唔好喊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T20:14:58.000Z","msg":"睇到你呢句我笑左出黎係咪我M過頭<br />\n不過多謝你個comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4deabbb5189a2e985ab3aafc2454281e447e0812","tid":1045820,"uid":240321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fce83c9548c6b27805f21e1b85fa253c33fc002a","tid":1045820,"uid":130093,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T19:58:29.000Z","msg":"毋忘初衷啦<br />\n<br />\n人生就好似跨越一座座高山咁，的確係辛苦，但係需要你一步步腳踏實地去行<br />\n<br />\n你試下全心全意擺副心機落去先，當試練又好、<br />\n<br />\n磨練又好，當你努力之後見到一個好靚嘅風景，再<br />\n<br />\n回頭望住自己昔日停留嘅山丘，就會好感激當初自<br />\n<br />\n己嘅堅持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T20:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我希望都好似你所講既一樣thanks"},{"pid":"1e06eeffccd4a2f24556b1d6d0da2bc295b88913","tid":1045820,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T20:16:48.000Z","msg":"用意志力"},{"pid":"209daaabc43308ce8c823fd5e680fdd7ea80fa36","tid":1045820,"uid":240321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e06eeffccd4a2f24556b1d6d0da2bc295b88913","tid":1045820,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T20:16:48.000Z","msg":"用意志力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T20:19:49.000Z","msg":"好抽象<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c67c328a576cb8eec277ca7b11e684335d6c3d2","tid":1045820,"uid":151865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T22:45:51.000Z","msg":"Tg我開解你"},{"pid":"0dee77677ce21e7d0493b3e57c0ca6cadbb06657","tid":1045820,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T23:04:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uCg2BoKiuOM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuCg2BoKiuOM&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=fcb7653c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uCg2BoKiuOM</a>"},{"pid":"27b595e91c9fe2e2ac4dd54864dbdb8d890ff2f6","tid":1045820,"uid":84922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T23:08:30.000Z","msg":"仲以為你中意畫畫結果比屋企人逼你放棄添<br />\n<br />\n講到尾，視覺傳藝係你揀既，證明至少你係有興趣既。又何來談的上逼自己做自己唔中意既野呢？<br />\n<br />\n最緊要既係你要知道咩令你開始唔中意原本你喜歡既野<br />\n例如d 19tutor，分數比你既壓力等等<br />\n<br />\n學識拋開佢地，做你想做既設計<br />\ntutor講既，岩聽就聽，唔岩就算<br />\n藝術呢d咁主觀既野，最多都係表達手法有高低，有咩理由會比人改到連原本既靈魂都冇左？<br />\n<br />\ntutor唔會改你既design，最多係比建議，落手改既人係你，亦都係你自己決定聽班tutor講既去將自己作品既靈魂換成人地既靈魂<br />\n<br />\n照你咁樣，人地講下就連自我就冇埋，咁不如一開始就放棄自我啦，咁就唔會有唔中意既野啦"},{"pid":"90a0db4b31f764e3a15f464f259fa44dc5ae063e","tid":1045820,"uid":52942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0dee77677ce21e7d0493b3e57c0ca6cadbb06657","tid":1045820,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T23:04:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uCg2BoKiuOM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuCg2BoKiuOM&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=fcb7653c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uCg2BoKiuOM</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T23:08:57.000Z","msg":"Have a Nice Day<br />\n原唱者：Bon Jovi<br />\n發行年：2005<br />\n<br />\nWhy, you wanna tell me how to live my life?<br />\n(奇怪，為什麼你能教我什麼是人生？)<br />\n<br />\nWho are you to tell me if it's black or white?<br />\n(你以為你是誰，你認為人生非黑即白？)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMama can you hear me? Try to understand.<br />\n(親愛的，你聽得到我嗎？試著了解吧)<br />\n<br />\nIs innocence the difference between a boy and a man.<br />\n(男人與男孩的差別，就是一顆單純的心)<br />\n<br />\nMy daddy lived the lie, it's just the price that he paid.<br />\n(我爸生活在謊言中，他為此付出代價)<br />\n<br />\nSacrificed his life, just slaving away.<br />\n(他永遠作不快樂的犧牲，奴役自己)<br />\n<br />\nOhhh, if there's one thing I hang on to,<br />\n(如果，我熱愛一樣東西)<br />\n<br />\nIt gets me through the night.<br />\n(我在夜晚也不會寂寞)<br />\n<br />\nI ain't gonna do what I don't want to,<br />\n(我不會浪費時間，作我不愛的事)<br />\n<br />\nI'm gonna live my life.<br />\n(這才叫作人生)<br />\n<br />\nThis lyrics is translated by Three Minute Passion<br />\n(本歌詞由三分鐘熱度部落格翻譯)<br />\n<br />\n Shining like a diamond, rolling with the dice,<br />\n(我像鑽石一樣發亮，雖然我不知道明天會如何)<br />\n<br />\nStanding on the ledge, show the wind how to fly.<br />\n(站在懸崖邊，我要告訴風怎麼飛)<br />\n<br />\nWhen the world gets in my face,<br />\n(當我看到這個世界時)<br />\n<br />\nI say, Have A Nice Day.<br />\n(我說：「祝你們快樂&hellip;」)<br />\n<br />\nHave A Nice Day<br />\n(「希望你們活得快樂&hellip;」)<br />\n<br />\nTake a look around you, nothing's what it seems<br />\n(看看你身邊的一切，許多事情都很虛偽)<br />\n<br />\nWe're living in a broken home of hopes and dreams,<br />\n(你的家，已經不是孕育夢想和希望的地方)<br />\n<br />\nLet me be the first to shake a helping hand.<br />\n(不過，我會伸出援手，喚醒你的熱情)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEverybody, pray enough to take a stand,<br />\n(各位，在心裡祈禱，然後站起來)<br />\n<br />\nI knocked on every door, on every dead end street,<br />\n(就算前方看不到出路，我仍會去找你)<br />\n<br />\nLooking for forgiveness,<br />\n(為你的無知，尋求原諒)<br />\n<br />\nwhat's left to believe?<br />\n(還有找回你殘存的信念)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">All lyrics translations from  Three Minutes Passion are original<br />\n(三分鐘熱度部落格內，所有翻譯歌詞皆為原創譯作)</span></span><br />\n<br />\nOhhh, if there's one thing I hang on to,<br />\n(當我的熱情被點燃時)<br />\n<br />\nIt gets me through the night.<br />\n(夜晚來臨，我也不會害怕)<br />\n<br />\nI ain't gonna do what I don't want to,<br />\n(為什麼要將寶貴的人生，浪費在自己不愛的事情上？)<br />\n<br />\nI'm gonna live my life.<br />\n(我要擁有自己的人生)<br />\n<br />\nShining like a diamond, rolling with the dice,<br />\n(像鑽石一樣發光，我寧願冒險也要追求自己所愛)<br />\n<br />\nStanding on the ledge, show the wind how to fly.<br />\n(我站在懸崖邊，讓風看看我怎麼飛)<br />\n<br />\nWhen the world gets in my face,<br />\n(當這個世界映入我眼中)<br />\n<br />\nI say, Have A Nice Day.<br />\n(我對他們說：祝你們快樂)<br />\n<br />\nHave A Nice Day.<br />\n(祝你們活得愉快)<br />\n<br />\nWhen The world keeps trying, to drag me down,<br />\n(很多人諷刺我，希望我像他們一樣氣餒)<br />\n<br />\nI've gotta raise my hands, gonna stand my ground.<br />\n(我會向他們揮手，這些人影響不了我)<br />\n<br />\nWell I say, Have A Nice Day.<br />\n(我會說：「你活得高興就好&hellip;」)<br />\n<br />\nHave A Nice Day<br />\n(「希望你活得快樂&hellip;」)<br />\n<br />\nHave A Nice Day<br />\n(「有個愉快的一天」)"},{"pid":"1365144d0c71dc909ab57995aa46389797717fe4","tid":1045820,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30e0cdb4c7e24d25f99023eaeb0cc4f46d444a0f","tid":1045820,"uid":240321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T19:36:41.000Z","msg":"第一次開post 錯台請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本因爲鐘意畫畫等讀左視覺傳意<br />\n但讀到中途發現學既野不如人意<br />\n交緊功課既主題都係比老師改完又改過，結果同原本自己既理念一啲都唔同<br />\n有同屋企人講過但佢地都叫我繼續讀落去只少拎張證書都好<br />\n<br />\n事到如今已經覺得做呢啲功課好痛苦<br />\n已經對GPA、功課進度之類無心裝載 好頹<br />\n但唔繼續落去又怕辜負屋企人既期望<br />\n<br />\n請問各位有無啲方法可以有動力迫做到一啲唔想做既事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬧下幾句都好 比我清醒下我應該要堅持既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T23:14:47.000Z","msg":"我覺得根本原因係你以為自己畫得好好，但係見過其他對手嘅實力之後，發覺自己原來都好廢，所以越讀越收皮<br />\n<br />\n基本上你未見過世面啫<br />\n<br />\n即係公開考試攞到好成績就以為自己好勁，唔知原來一山還有一山高"},{"pid":"d872992ab1f628b3631db15bb1ae446f379d8884","tid":1045820,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1365144d0c71dc909ab57995aa46389797717fe4","tid":1045820,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"